data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Move in ready Bungalow in St. Petersburg, No HOA!!  Entering the home you find the formal living room off to the right, with two bedrooms located to the left in the front of the home.  Crown molding through out the home.  Kitchen boasts of subway tile backsplash, butcher block counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  The kitchen leads you into the spacious family room where you can envision gatherings with family and friends.  Adjacent to the family room you will find french doors leading to a very spacious room that has a multipurpose use and can be used as an office or another bedroom. Lots of upgrades in this home including a newer roof, newer HVAC, new smart thermostat Echo B, newer Hot Water Heater, new carpet and newer luxury vinyl plank flooring.   The backyard has plenty of room for your weekend get togethers and is fully fenced in.  You can already envision out back those barbeque gatherings with your friends. Contact me today to see this gorgeous move in ready home.
